             <span id="ctl01_VEHomePageTextGeneral_HomePageText">
              <h1 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
               1 in a Million Cars is your premier resource for buying and selling classic cars. Our high-traffic site provides the enthusiast a unique opportunity to match rare antique vehicles, muscle cars, vintage sports cars, and all other classics to the right buyer and seller.
              </h1>
              <p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
               <a href="Vehicle/Search.aspx" mce_href="Vehicle/Search.aspx" style="color: #3333cc;">
                <img alt="Browse the Cars" height="35" mce_src="../images/browse.gif" src="../images/browse.gif" width="665"/>
               </a>
               Our searchable inventory will include a collection of rare and unique cars. I would like to invite you to spend some time searching through and viewing the ads, as you may be surprised by the treasures you might find.
              </p>
              <p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
               <a href="Vehicle/ListingEdit.aspx" mce_href="Vehicle/ListingEdit.aspx" style="color: #3333cc;">
                <img alt="Place an ad" height="35" mce_src="../images/placead.gif" src="../images/placead.gif" width="665"/>
               </a>
               Please take a moment and register, it is FREE and will only take a few minutes. Once you are registered you will be provided the exclusive opportunity to feature your car here for thousands of classic car aficionados.
              </p>
              <p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
               <a href="Vehicle/SearchDealer.aspx" mce_href="Vehicle/SearchDealer.aspx" style="color: #3333cc;">
                <img alt="Classic Auto Dealers" height="35" mce_src="../images/dealers.gif" src="../images/dealers.gif" width="665"/>
               </a>
               Visit our friends at these featured classic car dealerships to find even more fantastic deals. Please contact us to feature your vintage auto dealership on 1 in a Million Cars – The Internet’s #1 source for all things classic.
              </p>
              <h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">
               <a href="vehicle/Register.aspx" mce_href="vehicle/Register.aspx" style="color: #3333cc;">
                Register today to sell your 1 in a Million!
               </a>
              </h2>
             </span>
